---
---
<section class="steps-section py-5 position-relative z-1" style="background-color: transparent;">
  <div class="container py-5 reveal">
    <div class="text-center mb-5 pb-4">
      <span class="text-accent fw-bold text-uppercase tracking-wide small" style="letter-spacing: 2px;">El Proceso</span>
      <h2 class="display-4 text-dark mt-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">Tu Viaje Comienza</h2>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-4" style="width: 40px; height: 1px; background-color: #d97706;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row g-5 position-relative justify-content-center mt-2">

      <div class="col-md-4 text-center reveal">
        <div class="step-card-es position-relative p-5 h-100 bg-white overflow-hidden">
          <div class="step-numeral-es">I</div>
          <div class="position-relative pt-4" style="z-index:1;">
            <h4 class="text-dark fw-normal mt-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem;">Inscríbete Hoy</h4>
            <p class="text-muted fw-light mt-3 px-3">Pago único seguro. Sin suscripciones ni cargos ocultos jamás.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
        <div class="step-card-es position-relative p-5 h-100 bg-white overflow-hidden">
          <div class="step-numeral-es">II</div>
          <div class="position-relative pt-4" style="z-index:1;">
            <h4 class="text-dark fw-normal mt-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem;">Obtén Acceso</h4>
            <p class="text-muted fw-light mt-3 px-3">Acceso inmediato a todos los módulos premium y masterclasses de expertos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center reveal" style="transition-delay: 200ms">
        <div class="step-card-es position-relative p-5 h-100 bg-white overflow-hidden">
          <div class="step-numeral-es">III</div>
          <div class="position-relative pt-4" style="z-index:1;">
            <h4 class="text-dark fw-normal mt-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem;">Transfórmate</h4>
            <p class="text-muted fw-light mt-3 px-3">Practica a tu propio ritmo, donde y cuando quieras. Acceso de por vida.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @import '../styles/variables.scss';

  .step-card-es {
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #e7e5e4;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: $transition-smooth;
    &:hover {
      border-color: rgba(217,119,6,0.35);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: $shadow-md;
    }
  }

  .step-numeral-es {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    left: 20px;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    color: $color-accent;
    opacity: 0.15;
    user-select: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
</style>
